# Build output / VCS / editor noise
**/bin
**/obj
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.git
**/.vs
**/.idea
**/.vscode
**/*.user
**/TestResults
**/.DS_Store

# Secrets: never let a local .env leak into the build context (the API reads config via env vars at run time).
.env
**/.env

# Not needed by the API image build (context is the repo root; only src/ + the root manifests are used).
web/
tests/
docs/
.github/
.config/
**/*.md
